local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["masquerade"]={"masquerade","[,mɑːskə'reɪd; ,mæs-]","[,mæskə'red]","n.化妆舞会",'n.化妆舞会|||v.化装','A covering, as of cloth, that has openings for the eyes, entirely or partly conceals the face, and is worn especially at a masquerade ball.','（化妆舞会的）面具布做面具，上有孔可露出双眼、全部或部分地遮住面部，尤在假面舞会上佩戴','The robbers got into the bank by ||masquerading|| as security men.','劫匪假装成保安人员进入银行。'}
